<h2>What is Star Citizen Gimp?</h2>
<p>Star Citizen Gimp is a bot that notifies a subscriber whenever it detects new products on the RSI store as well as new articles from the comm link feed.</p>
<h2>Why would I use it?</h2>
<p>Because CIG is notorious for sending out no communication regarding promotions or hours after promotions and or content was released on the website the following use cases apply:</p>
<ul>
    <li>if you are sick of missing out on limited hull ship sales,</li>
    <li>if you want to be a contender to post FIRST on an article</li>
    <li>or if you simply have a problem like many other citizens in that you can't help but throw your wallet at the RSI store each time something new comes along then this is for you!</li>
</ul>
